-- Apple Sued Over IPhone 4 Reception Problems, Accused of False Advertising
-- Edvard Pettersson
-- 2010-07-01T01:11:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-01/apple-sued-over-iphone-4-reception-problems-accused-of-false-advertising.html

          
          
             Apple Inc. was sued by a consumer
who accused the company of false and misleading advertising
because of reception problems with the new iPhone 4.  
